For me, the decision to support PATCH/MERGE-type updates depends on my
caching support.

If adding &#39;partial updates&#39; will invalidate lots of other existing
cache items that need to be &#39;very fresh&#39;, then I opt out of adding
partial update support in order to cut down on &#39;out-of-phase&#39;
resources spread all over the Internets.

mca
